commit.message: Restrict our supported Pythons a bit.

Implement support for django cache framework.

Fixes #15.
Prevent sleep from being given a negative value
dont run tests with py2.6 as it is deprecated on travis-ci
Can disable time travel with NO_TIME_TRAVEL
Slightly cleaner time travel for testing
Pip no longer needs --use-mirrors on Travis, and supports >= 3.3.

Use getfullargspec in Python 3 so that we don't get exceptions.

We don't really care about the new information at all; all we need is positional
argument names and defaults. We just need it to not throw exceptions on us.

Fixes #14.
Bump to v1.0.1, and add wolf0403 to AUTHORS
Fixing issue where kwargs for memoized function lost when called with keyword syntax
tests moves to the tests directory, pep8, some whitespaces away :)
maxage -> max_age, pep8 conform, mutables removed from argument defaults
